# .ptk-scaffold — written by ptk-scaffold, removed by ptk-finalize.
# feature: ptk-modify
# language: markdown
# Frontier pattern (ERE): matches unfilled ptk:stub markers in this skill doc.
# Markdown has no stub() function — the marker is an HTML comment.
# Each section's body prose is the stub; ptk-execute fills it and removes the marker.
